sec.p:
Studies were selected if they met the following inclusion criteria:
Indexed articles between January 1st 1975 and December 13th 2013;
The search included the follow documents: letters to the editor, case presentations, case series, original research reports and reviews;
Clinical research articles in adults;
The following idioms were included: English, French, German and Spanish;

For exclusion criteria:
Articles published outside of proposed period;
Other published articles not specified by inclusion criteria;
Experimental clinical research articles;
Articles written by languages not specified by inclusion criteria;
Ritcher syndrome.
